Body: Description: Hi SUpport, We recently received an advisory ADV-2025-001 to update our server and tried running an live update. However, We are receiving an error " An error occured. Hash does not match" at the time of the update. Kindly help us resolve this.
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux
Invitation updated. Attendees: No attendees listed
Invitation updated. Attendees: Andre Le Roux, Rahul Pandey
What We've Learned Updated: Customer's firewall was blocking traffic between EPP Server and our liveupdate server. We found this after testing for communication from the EPP Server's backend.
